imdb.plot outline: Meet Karli Henriquez, MTV Tr3s' hot new Angelina VJ! Follow Karli as she journeys through the city of Angels each week and dishes the celebrity 411. From the red carpet to la calle, Karli's got the low-down on the latest Latino L.A. trends. Join Karli as she brings us exclusive interviews with your favorite artists and actors, and all other personalities making their mark in the city of Angels.
